data.description: Welcome to this spacious and inviting four-bedroom, two-bathroom home. One of the standout features of this property is its fully fenced backyard. It offers a secure and private space for outdoor activities, allowing you to enjoy the fresh air and entertain guests. It is a great place for children and pets to play safely. The location of the house is highly convenient, being in close proximity to Carrol Park, the Alamosa High School, a range of local shops, restaurants, and services. This house is a must see!!
